Package edu.umd.cs.guitar.event

Package for events supported by GUITAR.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GEvent
    Abstract class for all events in GUITAR.
    GEventConfigurable
    Interface to be implemented by events that want to be informed of the GEventConfiguration.
    GEventConfiguration
    Interface to be implemented by classes that contain data for configuring GEvents.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventManager
    A singleton class to manage all events supported by GUITAR
    GThreadEvent
    Abstract class for all GUITAR events requiring to run in a separate thread.
